Name: Fran

Instructions: complete 21-15-9 reps of thrusters and Pull-ups.
Instructions_Clean: Complete 21-15-9 repetitions of thrusters and pull-ups.
TargetStimulus: High-intensity sprint with pulling and barbell cycling.
Scaling_Tiers: {"Beginner": "Complete 10-7-4 reps of Thrusters and Pull-ups. - Beginner: lighter loads, banded/assistance, reduced volume.", "Intermediate": "Complete 21-15-9 reps of Thrusters and Pull-ups. - Intermediate: moderate loads, standard scaling.", "Advanced": "Complete 21-15-9 reps of Thrusters and Pull-ups. - Advanced: Rx or add weight/tempo.", "Limited Equipment": "Complete 21-15-9 reps of Thrusters and Pull-ups. - Limited equipment: substitute barbells with dumbbells/kettlebells, row with running."}
ScalingOptions: Reduce reps, lighten load, or modify gymnastics (e.g., banded pull-ups, lighter KB, shortened run distances).
